ates using the premium index method, comparing perpetual prices to spot prices every second and applying an 8-hour Time-Weighted Average Price (TWAP). The funding rate is capped at ±0.75% per interval, with payments occurring at 00:00, 08:00, and 16:00 UTC. Binance's deep BNB liquidity ensures minimal slippage during rate settlements, typically processing over $500M in daily perpetual volume for this pair."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
